snippet: Chancellor George Osborne held up Britain's recent strong pace of economic growth as vindication of his austerity programme that came under fire from the International Monetary Fund last year....

headline.print_headline: Osborne Touts UK Recovery on Return to Sceptical IMF
headline.main: Osborne Touts UK Recovery on Return to Sceptical IMF

lead_paragraph: Chancellor George Osborne held up Britain's recent strong pace of economic growth as vindication of his austerity programme that came under fire from the International Monetary Fund last year.
